                     <!-- ********* <layoutDesc> ********* -->
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="1" writtenLines="11">
                           <p>Written in predominantly square script with a few round exceptions,
                              the text is engraved upon a smoothed surface. This surface is chipped
                              in the lower left corner and on the right side. The text is surrounded
                              by a rectangular, incised frame painted over in red. Lines one, six,
                              and nine are partially painted over in red, while lines five, seven,
                              and eight are partially painted over in green. Line three is
                              completely painted in red, and line eleven is totally painted
                              green.</p>
                        </layout>
